In re Resignation of Hunter.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hunter. (1993), 66 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 92-2472 Submitted January 6, 1993 Decided January 7, 1993.)

The resignation of Joyce D. Hunter as an attorney, Registration No. 0038512, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
